name: TVPV NV CVRV
description:
#7 “under.stage” collection explores the underground events environment of northeastern Brazil.

rapper "biggie n" in olinda - pernambuco – brazil, singing "tapa na cara" at the historic show where happened the first presentation of *sulicidio and filming the music video 999 of rapper "baco exu do blues"

*historical diss of rappers “diomedes chinaski” and “baco exu do blues” against the musical system, that centralizes the attentions in a single region of the country

olinda- pernambuco - brazil - 2016
